name: r/Morocco
description: The flag of Morocco made by the r/Morocco subreddit. It includes, the country's Motto: الله، ٱلْوَطَن، ٱلْمَلِك (God,Homeland,King),The Hassan II mosque,Moroccan architecture (Zellige),And a collaboration with r/Pokemon which depicts Pikachu wearing traditionnal Moroccan clothes (Jellaba and Fez)
